From 45f484025e21c86126dde0a0d6fd388ef5776065 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 10:46:28 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(access): register invite-keys on root app + harden deploy
 probe

Prod was serving a build without invite-keys (session still required only
portalAuthCode; GET /api/access/invite-keys returned Fastify Route not found).

- Register invite-keys GET/POST/PATCH/revoke on the root Fastify instance with
  preHandler: requireAdmin (avoid nested plugin registration)
- Add PATCH updateInviteKey for rename / project edits
- Expose features.inviteKeys on /api/access/health
- Fail permissions-image deploy if invite-keys returns 404 instead of 401
- Pass GIT_SHA into the image for health revision
---
 .github/workflows/permissions-image.yml | 28 +++++++--
 Dockerfile                              |  2 +
 src/access/inviteKeys.ts                | 76 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/api/access.ts                       | 71 +++++++++++++++--------
 src/contracts/portal-access.ts          |  9 +++
 5 files changed, 158 insertions(+), 28 deletions(-)

